{"tid":2074184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中美角力】特朗普：因中美貿易協議 未就新疆問題制裁中國","createTime":"2020-06-22T02:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T19:29:51.000Z","uid":51665,"like":11,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3d71f6abec01fe2ba6cbc19a7d7bb83cbd1e9a15","tid":2074184,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2676382/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%20%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%B1%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2676382%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%258A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%259B%25A0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%2520%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=c077472e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2676382/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%20%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%B1%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a><br />\n美國總統特朗普承認，為了中美貿易協議，尚未就新疆問題制裁中國。<br />\n<br />\n美國Axios周日報道，特朗普上周五被問到，為何尚未就中國修建針對維吾爾族和其它少數民族的「再教育營」時，他稱因為這樣做將影響與中國的貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，「我們正處在一項重大貿易協議的中間階段」，「我達成了一項非常棒的協議，總值2500億美元的貨品採購」。他又認為美國對中國加徵關稅，這比任何制裁都要嚴厲得多。<br />\n美國前國家安全顧問博爾頓（John Bolton）在即將出版的新書中稱，特朗普尋求中國國家主席習近平的幫助以贏得連任，又曾認可新疆的拘留營。特朗普否認這一指控。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上周三簽署《維吾爾人權政策法》，將允許華府制裁涉及壓迫新疆維吾爾族的中國官員，引起中國反彈，促美糾正錯誤，否則將堅決反制。<br />\n<br />\nmolamola！大豆trump+china joe=香港／台灣玩撚猿喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890ad8faa9d8cdb95bb77b3e7eda571031f1165d","tid":2074184,"uid":176313,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"dllm....即係香港都唔會制裁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331569aad55005c6054b1fe9b7be7baee7e10bd4","tid":2074184,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"890ad8faa9d8cdb95bb77b3e7eda571031f1165d","tid":2074184,"uid":176313,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"dllm....即係香港都唔會制裁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"美國淨係會保台灣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e40281954e7aa55d846587cb7e0583ce71dad5f","tid":2074184,"uid":51665,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"國安法又可以加辣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab6f807ee0b5dc58e210739eee49793c9159b86","tid":2074184,"uid":294121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:32:20.000Z","msg":"下個就到香港做condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408525655d6ac07c8b0498819e9bd3e7b4896985","tid":2074184,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"GG<br />\n要學做小粉紅了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d838444cf134b1a13ed832a2697c0281848dec1","tid":2074184,"uid":51665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHgJ8Xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHgJ8Xa.jpg&h=6520dd2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個世界上無嘢可以擋得住人民幣嘅誘惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eeefd567487c501f707e